---
title: Herby Halloumi, Chicken & Roast Veggie Salad with Garlic Aioli & Flaked Almonds
description: Here’s a hearty vegetarian meal that brings inspiration from across the globe to your plate. Flavourful Mediterranean halloumi
meets chicken and roasted vegetables tossed with mild spices, and there’s a tangy aioli and toasted almonds to finish it off.

